version_description:
New version 1.6.1 is released globally!
- Global release: play our game from anywhere in the world;
- 11 new languages: find your preferred translation in the game settings;
- Etruscan Tombs: Encounter fallen Etruscan warriors, loot treasures & find copper;
- To improve optimization, enemy remains are now deleted when leaving a map;
- Gold for gems purchase opportunity added;
- Grand optimization for faster game startup loading.
Welcome to Rome! Join us in Discord for discussions or to get tips!

